                      Golf Holidays with Golf Escapes  
                   
         
           
              Welcome to the Golf Escapes website...you'll find hundreds of great deals on a  golf holiday in Portugal ,  golf holiday in Spain ,  golf holiday in Turkey ,  golf holidays in Cyprus ,  golf holiday in Northern Cyprus ,  golf holiday in Morocco ,  golf holidays in Dubai ,  golf holidays in Egypt ,  UK Golf Breaks & UK Golf Holidays ,  Golf Breaks & Golf Holidays in England ,  Golf Breaks & Golf Holidays in Wales ,  Golf Breaks & Golf Holidays in Scotland  and  weekend golf breaks in the UK . 
 Since starting up in 2002, Golf Escapes have sent over 25000 happy golfers on some fantastic  golf breaks in Portugal ,  golf breaks in Spain ,  golf breaks in Turkey ,  golf breaks in Cyprus ,  golf breaks in North Cyprus ,  golf breaks in Morocco ,  golf breaks in Dubai  &  golf breaks in Egypt . We also offer  weekend golf breaks in England ,  weekend golf breaks in Scotland ,  weekend golf breaks in Wales  and well as many more  weekend golf breaks in the UK .  
 If you are looking for a deal on an  Algarve golf holiday ,  Lisbon golf holiday ,  Madeira golf holiday ,  Tenerife golf holiday ,  Gran Canaria golf holiday ,  Fuerteventura golf holiday ,  Northern Cyprus golf holiday ,  Morocco golf holiday ,  Costa del Sol golf holiday ,  Almeria golf holiday ,  Costa Brava golf holiday ,  Murcia golf holiday ,  Costa de la Luz golf holiday ,  Majorca golf holiday ,  Belek golf holiday ,  Dubai golf holiday ,   Cyprus golf holiday ,  Egypt golf holiday ,  UK Golf Breaks ,  Golf Breaks in England ,  Golf Breaks in Scotland ,  Golf Breaks in Wales  we can offer discounted golf packages in all these destinations. 
 Our sales team are familiar with all properties and golf courses featured on the website, so for advice and to take advantage of our combined 50+ years in the travel industry, please feel free to call us on 01342 811777 or send us  an email . 
 Please note: We are a fully bonded tour operator which ensures that any money paid to us is protected either through our ABTA or ATOL licences.  
           
                     
               
              
           
          
       
     
     
       
          
             
                
                   
                      
                         
                           
